WEBVTT

1
00:03:15.030 --> 00:03:19.720 
又冷又干的空气使它们无法解冻
The air is just too cold and too dry for it to do so.

2
00:03:24.680 --> 00:03:28.280 
阳光把它们直接变成了水蒸气
The sun's rays turn it straight into vapour.

3
00:03:28.280 --> 00:03:30.320 
它们升华了
It evaporates.

4
00:03:39.390 --> 00:03:42.600 
可是这是唯一的水源
But it is the only source of water,

5
00:03:42.670 --> 00:03:45.490 
所以双峰驼只能吃雪
so Bactrian camels eat it.

